body: if you'd look closely at the pages where the titles are written (pg. 14 here, pg. 3 there), they have different kanjis, one was kainyuu miko (怪乳巫女) and this is hyakka nyuuran (百華乳乱). I guess it was renamed after tank release. so yeah, there's nothing to fix.
